Question 7:
Show first name, last name, and the full province name of each patient.
Example: 'Ontario' instead of 'ON'

Solution:

SELECT 
    patients.first_name,
    patients.last_name,
    province_names.province_name
FROM 
    patients
JOIN 
    province_names
ON 
    patients.province_id = province_names.province_id;
